                <div class="prog-tile" onclick="enterCurrentProgram()">
                  <div class="prog-ico">
                    <svg class="glyph lg"><use href="#g-building"/></svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="prog-name">Vendor Cleanup Program</div>
                  <div class="prog-desc">Ingest vendor documents directly from Google Drive. Classify signals, compute risk posture, and surface renewal obligations across your entire vendor portfolio.</div>
